name: Bitcoin Pizza 79715
description: This NFT entitles the owner to claim the Bitcoin Pizza #79715 inscribed on the Bitcoin Blockchain. Ordinals are digital assets inscribed on Satoshis, the lowest denomination of Bitcoin (BTC). Please open a Support Ticket in our Discord to Claim the Pizza. In order to claim the Ordinal, a compatible Bitcoin address is required. Please follow this Tutorial to Setup a compatible Bitcoin Wallet: https://docs.raredough.com/receiving-bitcoin-ordinals
